Quick historical overview
========================================================
transition: rotate

<br>

* 18th century, Munehisa Homma - Japanese rice trader of financial instruments
  * Hence other name: *Japanese candlestick chart*
* 1996 West: Steve Nison - *Japanese Candlestick Charting Techniques*
  * More likely: candle charts developed in the late 1800s
* Nowadays used in stock analysis


