Candlestick encoding
========================================================
transition: fade

```{r, echo=TRUE, warnings = FALSE, eval= FALSE, error = FALSE, include=TRUE}

df %>%
  plot_ly(x = ~Date,
          type  = "candlestick",
          open  = ~Open,
          close = ~Close,
          high  = ~High,
          low   = ~Low)
```




